text: "Tukoh Taka" is a reggaeton/pop 2022 FIFA Fan Festival anthem by Trinidadian- American rapper Nicki Minaj featuring musicians Maluma and Myriam Fares, released on November 18, 2022. It was released by FIFA for the official 2022 FIFA World Cup soundtrack. ==References== Category:Nicki Minaj songs Category:2022 songs Category:Pop songs
